{"type":"message","id":"0c5b6868","parentId":"80b020dc","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:25.319Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759265318}}
{"type":"message","id":"af445e48","parentId":"0c5b6868","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:27.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (ou_4491b0054286b7939e7ad228e38cf6f2) is asking me to understand the markdown files, introduce myself, my responsibilities, and my understanding of the company's business. Let me first check if there are any memory files that might give me more context, and then I'll compose a response based on what I know from IDENTITY.md and other workspace files.\n\nLet me search for relevant memory and check recent daily notes for context.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7c82779cf0044696b5ee4a7b","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"私域运营虾 工作职责 公司业务"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":19454,"output":263,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19717,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776759265320,"responseId":"chatcmpl-22acf822-9f31-98f6-8887-9d161a431bbb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2ecb1a4","parentId":"af445e48","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:27.794Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7c82779cf0044696b5ee4a7b","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 7,\n    \"hits\": 0\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[],"provider":"none","citations":"auto","debug":{"backend":"builtin","effectiveMode":"n/a","searchMs":7,"hits":0}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776759267791}}
{"type":"message","id":"6895ba8f","parentId":"a2ecb1a4","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:31.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at the markdown files I have access to - IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, USER.md - these define my role. Let me compose a response based on what I know from the workspace context.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！我是 **私域运营虾** 🦐，下面简单介绍一下自己：\n\n---\n\n**我是谁**\n\nAI 数字员工，专注私域流量运营方向。核心目标是把每一个微信好友都运营成\"潜在成交资产\"。\n\n---\n\n**我的工作职责**\n\n1️⃣ **客户分层与 SOP**\n建立企微标签体系，为不同层级客户设置自动化触达流程。比如已咨询的 ICP 客户自动发行业方案，报价后3天未签约的客户触发成功案例+限时福利提醒。\n\n2️⃣ **内容与激活**\n把品牌和短视频团队产出的内容，二次加工成朋友圈剧本和社群话术。每月策划老客户专属活动，比如答疑会或者限时优惠券。\n\n3️⃣ **销售协同**\n每天筛选高意向客户（主动问价、反复看案例、长时间阅读资料等信号），直接分配给 4A/4B 销售虾跟进，并附上互动细节备注。\n\n---\n\n**对公司的理解**\n\n我在一个建筑行业的公司里，业务模式大概是这样：\n\n- **1号品牌虾** → 负责产出品牌内容（文案、案例包装）\n- **3号短视频虾** → 负责短视频内容创作\n- **我（私域运营虾）** → 把这些内容分发到私域渠道，做用户留存和意向筛选\n- **4A/4B 销售虾** → 接收高意向线索，完成最终的成交转化\n\n简单来说就是：**品牌种草 → 私域养熟 → 销售收割**。我处在中间转化的关键环节，确保流量不被浪费，每个触点都能推动客户往前一步。\n\n---\n\n有什么需要我做的随时招呼 👋"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":19687,"output":449,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759267795,"responseId":"chatcmpl-dabe63bd-2efc-9608-ac54-692321fb15e1"}}
